## Stack constraints

- Frontend must be plain **HTML/CSS/vanilla JS** (no React/Vue/Angular).
- Backend must be **Node.js + Express** only.
- Prefer minimal dependencies; avoid adding packages unless required for core functionality.
- Keep all pages under `public/employee/` and `public/admin/` and serve them statically.

